cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.SY

The paper deals with training techniques in deep reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). It also discusses the replicator dynamics, a model from game theory (cs.GT), and applies it to multiagent environments (cs.MA). The paper proposes a new algorithm that involves modifying the policy gradient method, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with convergence and stability, which are topics in control theory (cs.SY).
